---
title: EventBus - Vestige Subscription Lifecycle
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Battle
    participant EventBus
    participant vestige as vestige : AttunistGambitVestige
    participant echoing as echoing : EchoingStrikeVestige
    participant AchievementSystem

    Battle ->> vestige: onBattleStart(battle, state)
    vestige ->> EventBus: subscribe(UnitDefeatedEvent handler, Battle scope)

    Battle ->> echoing: onBattleStart(battle, state)
    echoing ->> EventBus: subscribe(ResonanceFieldTriggeredEvent handler, Battle scope)

    AchievementSystem ->> EventBus: subscribe(UnitDefeatedEvent handler, Run scope)
    AchievementSystem ->> EventBus: subscribe(BreakTriggeredEvent handler, Run scope)

    Battle ->> EventBus: emit(UnitDefeatedEvent)
    EventBus ->> vestige: handler(UnitDefeatedEvent)
    EventBus ->> AchievementSystem: handler(UnitDefeatedEvent)

    Battle ->> EventBus: emit(ResonanceFieldTriggeredEvent)
    EventBus ->> echoing: handler(ResonanceFieldTriggeredEvent)

    Battle ->> EventBus: clearBattleScope()
    Note over EventBus: Battle-scoped handlers removed. Run-scoped handlers survive.
